Spain Reduces Forecast For 2011 Public Debt, Europa Press Says

-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 
2011-04-29T06:18:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-29/spain-reduces-forecast-for-2011-public-debt-europa-press-says.html
The Spanish government reduced its
forecast for the country’s public debt this year to 67.2 percent
of the economy, Europa Press said, citing a government reported
filed with the European Commission in Brussels.   The government previously forecast the debt would reach
68.7 percent when it set this year’s budget, the agency said.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
